Package com.amplifyframework.api.rest

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RestBehavior
    REST behaviors which include the family of HTTP verbs (GET, POST, etc.).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RestOperation
    A RestOperation is an API operation which returns a REST results.
    RestOperationRequest
    Request object used by the RestOperation.
    RestOptions
    Request against REST endpoint.
    RestOptions.Builder
    A utility that can be used to configure and construct immutable instances of the RestOptions.Builder, by chaining fluent configuration method calls.
    RestResponse
    Response from rest request.
    RestResponse.Code
    Status code of the response.
    RestResponse.Data
    Data representing the response of the HTTP request.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HttpMethod
    Enum of REST operation types.
